com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.internal

Class AsyncCache<TKey,TValue>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.internal.AsyncCache<TKey,TValue>

  • public final class AsyncCache<TKey,TValue>
extends java.lang.Object
    Cache which supports asynchronous value initialization for the Azure DocumentDB database service Java SDK. It ensures that for given key only single initialization function is running at any point in time.
